&gt; <i>People who prioritize their health are more likely to have friends who prioritize their health. And so on.</i>
&gt;
&gt; <i>We become like the people we choose to be around.</i><p>I&#x27;m not convinced that that&#x27;s it. It&#x27;s more likely that the first person who got solar installed talked to their neighbors about it, and the neighbors were convinced. It&#x27;s not like after you move to a neighborhood, you&#x27;re really choosing anything after that point about your neighbors.
